Usage: addSdpGroupMember [-help] -group <groupName> -object {objName(s)}
                         [-orientation <orientStr>] [-before <refObject> | -after <refObject>]

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
-after <refObject>           # add object after reference object
                             # (string, optional)
-before <refObject>          # add object before reference object
                             # (string, optional)
-group <groupName>           # name of the group (string, required)
-object {objName(s)}         # name of the object to be added to sdp group
                             # (string, required)
-orientation <orientStr>     # orientation to be set to the object
                             # (string, optional)